{"tid":2087550,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"6月30日黃家駒死忌冇人開post？","createTime":"2020-06-30T17:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T09:24:43.000Z","uid":53766,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c89460c8724caab32240e92a449df314ceeebfcd","tid":2087550,"uid":53766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"原諒我這一生不羈放縱愛自由<br />\n也會怕有一天會跌倒 背棄了理想<br />\n誰人都可以 那會怕有一天只你共我<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQ98BhqF9QU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQ98BhqF9QU&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c29719ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQ98BhqF9QU</a><br />\n<br />\n今天只有殘留的軀殼<br />\n迎接光輝歲月<br />\n風雨中抱緊自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HDsGgVxlX6I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHDsGgVxlX6I&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b3644e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HDsGgVxlX6I</a><br />\n<br />\n但每分秒使我生厭這都市現狀　沒法相信終會拋棄這荒島<br />\nWoo Ho Woo　Woo Ho Woo　面對歪曲的制度<br />\nWoo Ho Woo　Woo Ho Woo　問那方是我家土<br />\n求講給我知<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zXglsI9oH18\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzXglsI9oH18&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f55c534f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zXglsI9oH18</a><br />\n<br />\n只有頑強　明日路縱會更徬徨<br />\n疲倦慣了再沒感覺　別在可惜計較什麼<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7o7tq7WLXR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7o7tq7WLXR4&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=9ab2eeb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7o7tq7WLXR4</a><br />\n<br />\n風騷的政客仍舊是故作公正<br />\n超級的戰鬥仍舊在咄咄進逼<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9o3Q3qSdlkU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9o3Q3qSdlkU&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4814083e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9o3Q3qSdlkU</a><br />\n<br />\n追逐一生的理想<br />\n命運讓你我呼叫<br />\nwoo<br />\n點解點解<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4AVHlehY2kc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4AVHlehY2kc&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=a492e762\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4AVHlehY2kc</a><br />\n<br />\n世界正越變越糊塗　太多慾望的迫壓<br />\n我已厭倦了在從前　常被受騙<br />\n可否衝破眼前這裝扮　可否衝破以前那顫抖的歲月 道別舊日落寞現在堅守我自信<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gxAtr7HqGIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgxAtr7HqGIE&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwObr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=5ad19759\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gxAtr7HqGIE</a>"},{"pid":"96bf0aebb4386771f12af5b4f38060c8c58f30d1","tid":2087550,"uid":221265,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:11:56.000Z","msg":"同香港同月同日死"},{"pid":"88a7110ed2dd0a9f935940bb5af4bd407cc26cfc","tid":2087550,"uid":53766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"家駒真係走得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由, 和平, 抗爭, 繼續革命, 歪曲既制度, 黑人..."},{"pid":"201d380798e6337117d47fec70ecd5a184df44a2","tid":2087550,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不死傳奇"},{"pid":"950c2450ec2c1a459abe369e0f89eab28658d4a4","tid":2087550,"uid":177873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b6c97a442a131d661bbabe914a1d9cc28d8f03","tid":2087550,"uid":5255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:17:47.000Z","msg":"家駒，miss u"},{"pid":"85ce9371dd6c319a324631945032beebfffc1c88","tid":2087550,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"家駒，永遠懷念您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets